n of Assam\u2019s National Register of Citizens (NRC).Population census is not a boring exercise. It is an exercise that helps to provide people the benefits of the government schemes. National Population Register (NPR) will help government solve many issues in the country.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/aadhaar-may-be-used-to-verify-secc-beneficiaries/articleshow/70794289.cms  at  "}